attributes.Long form description: The student starts the task by unscrewing and disassembling the wheels from the rolling cart, then he proceeds to unscrew and remove each tray's brackets in order to disassemble them, later, he unscrews and disassembles the sidebars and finally he detaches the base frames to complete the task.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the wheels on the right.
The student disassembles the left wheels.
The student disassembles the top grid tray.
The student disassembles the tray in the middle.
The student disassembles the bottom tray.
The student unscrews the right screws of the side bars.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The screw wasn't supposed to fall to the floor.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the left screws of the side bar.
The student disassembles the third side bar.
The student disassembles the fourth side bar.
The student disassembles the black base frame.
